@KafkaApiService_HostAddress = http://localhost:7070

### Health Check
GET {{KafkaApiService_HostAddress}}/api/kafka/health

### Send generic message
POST {{KafkaApiService_HostAddress}}/api/kafka/message
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "topic": "test-topic",
  "data": "Hello Kafka from API!",
  "key": "test-key-123"
}

### Send matricula log
POST {{KafkaApiService_HostAddress}}/api/kafka/matricula-log
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "matriculaId": 1001,
  "estudianteId": 5001,
  "seccionId": 2001,
  "costo": 250.75,
  "metodoPago": "Tarjeta de Crédito",
  "estado": "COMPLETADA",
  "fechaMatricula": "2024-11-14T10:30:00Z",
  "eventType": "MATRICULA_CREADA",
  "message": "Matrícula procesada exitosamente"
}

### Send email event
POST {{KafkaApiService_HostAddress}}/api/kafka/email-event
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "matriculaId": 1001,
  "to": "estudiante@example.com",
  "subject": "Confirmación de Matrícula",
  "body": "Su matrícula ha sido procesada exitosamente",
  "sentDate": "2024-11-14T10:31:00Z",
  "eventType": "EMAIL_SENT"
}
